{"tid":568772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢見到屍體，有冇ching識得解夢？","createTime":"2018-02-22T06:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T11:52:19.000Z","uid":84775,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7755f6568b2e502420758808052db0a183b29426","tid":568772,"uid":84775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:04:30.000Z","msg":"話說尋晚我發夢，夢見自己喺度check email, 而內容就係話有個人死咗，叫人悼念，死者個名好似係叫&ldquo;黃遙玲&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n之後我即時收到個包裹，一打開就係個死屍，而死屍個樣被橙色頸巾包遮住<br />\n<br />\n死者皮膚偏白，第1吓望個陣未感覺驚，但望到橙色頸巾就冇啦啦，睇到條屍入咗箱個刻係點樣<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣個包裹其他位置封晒，剩低頭嗰面位置未封，之後有部手機係包裹上面，播住片，片入面係一個女人樣，佢擘大隻眼之後反白眼咁合埋，同時條死屍雙眼同片做嘅嘢一樣<br />\n<br />\n點解我會發埋啲咁嘅前㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e11875b620d652e21b1db28fd21277d02d1141","tid":568772,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14ddde4b58bb6bab58329c4f3a0ec0646a85cdb4","tid":568772,"uid":84775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e11875b620d652e21b1db28fd21277d02d1141","tid":568772,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"普通身材，用超大個長方形紙皮箱包住"},{"pid":"a5d2acc688a94e9f0e522fbb1b7c3a4cc1d28552","tid":568772,"uid":136467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08fbe313b92c5f5c917a010120090741b518dc53","tid":568772,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14ddde4b58bb6bab58329c4f3a0ec0646a85cdb4","tid":568772,"uid":84775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e11875b620d652e21b1db28fd21277d02d1141","tid":568772,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"普通身材，用超大個長方形紙皮箱包住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"發夢見到肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔敢訓番"},{"pid":"1aa90424172b071d13a8ef1c4848a232e3b40d1a","tid":568772,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:15:30.000Z","msg":"見屍體，主長壽富。《周公解夢》<br />\n見死屍，主長壽，吉。《周公解夢》<br />\n為人抬屍，有人請。《周公解夢》"},{"pid":"8af4cf9d2708c7616b36a0d73ef2b12ef53d5846","tid":568772,"uid":84775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa90424172b071d13a8ef1c4848a232e3b40d1a","tid":568772,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:15:30.000Z","msg":"見屍體，主長壽富。《周公解夢》<br />\n見死屍，主長壽，吉。《周公解夢》<br />\n為人抬屍，有人請。《周公解夢》"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"我上網睇到又話會行衰運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f010b0ff68feeae61cac7b2a44950d39e478e7d9","tid":568772,"uid":10821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"自首啦"},{"pid":"24b8730ec4ad9286bc58c4f213c360ec58ac6cf6","tid":568772,"uid":84775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:21:59.000Z","msg":"有冇人發過類似嘅夢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed73ec70c4d2af8c59f2c6b1a37dbbaa80f817f9","tid":568772,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08fbe313b92c5f5c917a010120090741b518dc53","tid":568772,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14ddde4b58bb6bab58329c4f3a0ec0646a85cdb4","tid":568772,"uid":84775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49e11875b620d652e21b1db28fd21277d02d1141","tid":568772,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:12:48.000Z","msg":"普通身材，用超大個長方形紙皮箱包住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"發夢見到肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔敢訓番"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:30:31.000Z","msg":"笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c708459b311aa3941c435bce45f01e3d16fd01f","tid":568772,"uid":129648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f010b0ff68feeae61cac7b2a44950d39e478e7d9","tid":568772,"uid":10821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"自首啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"啟撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bc35dff2fe146928b44b37a914a3a9c99e49d63","tid":568772,"uid":129648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c708459b311aa3941c435bce45f01e3d16fd01f","tid":568772,"uid":129648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f010b0ff68feeae61cac7b2a44950d39e478e7d9","tid":568772,"uid":10821,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"自首啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:41:59.000Z","msg":"啟撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:42:21.000Z","msg":"笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8582f1f06364f9bc40b5df69d7c2c1e44e2bff25","tid":568772,"uid":33464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"以前睇解夢書 話夢見屍體分兩種<br />\n<br />\n見到認識既人 代表你感到不幸<br />\n<br />\n見到唔識既人 代表你感到幸福"},{"pid":"dc5fba3f907f642afb3884e30030c36d57d422eb","tid":568772,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:56:48.000Z","msg":"之前發夢自己坐巴士上層第一行，撞車死左，跟住畫面黑曬<br />\n下個畫面就係夢見阿媽同大家姊好似平日咁傾計，望一望日曆發現係自己死前既一日，既刻好傷心好唔捨得，跟住就醒左"},{"pid":"1d760e4f0927c81fa0991a9143ae97ecf30157ee","tid":568772,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"咁你識唔識邊個係黃遙玲？<br />\n有冇呢個人嘅新聞？<br />\n冇的話 黃遙玲個名俾你感覺係邊個？<br />\n我唔識解夢 <br />\n但夢入面嘅嘢好多時同潛意識、生活體驗有關<br />\n我都發過好多奇怪夢，所以有興趣<br />\n例如點解條巾係橙色？ 橙色對你嚟講有咩意義？<br />\n你睇橙色第一時間會有咩感覺？<br />\n個女人似唔似你識嘅人？<br />\n個女人死唔一定就係現實有人死<br />\n可能只係個女人只一種象徵<br />\n用死去呈現你對佢嘅感覺<br />\n我自己係咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我細個試過發夢學校係煉獄"},{"pid":"fd876d5916681d7de41619fa1fa2d45af8796ba5","tid":568772,"uid":84775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d760e4f0927c81fa0991a9143ae97ecf30157ee","tid":568772,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"咁你識唔識邊個係黃遙玲？<br />\n有冇呢個人嘅新聞？<br />\n冇的話 黃遙玲個名俾你感覺係邊個？<br />\n我唔識解夢 <br />\n但夢入面嘅嘢好多時同潛意識、生活體驗有關<br />\n我都發過好多奇怪夢，所以有興趣<br />\n例如點解條巾係橙色？ 橙色對你嚟講有咩意義？<br />\n你睇橙色第一時間會有咩感覺？<br />\n個女人似唔似你識嘅人？<br />\n個女人死唔一定就係現實有人死<br />\n可能只係個女人只一種象徵<br />\n用死去呈現你對佢嘅感覺<br />\n我自己係咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我細個試過發夢學校係煉獄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:50:22.000Z","msg":"我完全唔識嗰個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 係夢入面，感覺佢個名好old school<br />\n<br />\n我見唔到個女人個樣，因為佢個樣比條橙色頸巾套住，只係見到佢偏白額頭同啡色頭髮<br />\n<br />\n夢入面又冇咩特別感覺，又唔係話好驚，只係覺得有啲恐怖，點解要寄條屍比我，但唔寄比其他人（夢入面問過其他睇過email嘅人）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係好耐冇試發夢，一嚟就嚟啲咁嘅夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7a16aec2e893084a67721b9bd816f76a54c6a6","tid":568772,"uid":84775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8582f1f06364f9bc40b5df69d7c2c1e44e2bff25","tid":568772,"uid":33464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"以前睇解夢書 話夢見屍體分兩種<br />\n<br />\n見到認識既人 代表你感到不幸<br />\n<br />\n見到唔識既人 代表你感到幸福"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"但我唔覺得自己幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}